<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 38. Distribution map of the new Glyphidrilus species from Thailand. Filled hexagon: Glyphidrilus vesper sp. n., Open trapezoid: Glyphidrilus wararamensis sp. n., Filled trapezoid: Glyphidrilus trangensis sp. n., Filled star: Glyphidrilus kratuensis sp. n." , "Figure 36. Morphology of the holotype (CUMZ 3266) of Glyphidrilus vesper sp. n., showing the A external ventral and B internal dorsal views." , "Figure 35. Photographs showing the A and B type locality of Glyphidrilus vesper sp. n. in a muddy swamp near the Thilorsu Waterfall, Umphang, Tak and C coloration of newly collected paratype CUMZ 3267 just after the first preservation step in 30 % (v / v) ethanol." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27653" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27651" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/27650" .

